data.description: Located only a few minutes away from Breaux Bridge and I-10, this home offers easy access to all that Breaux Bridge has to offer along with convenience for anyone commuting to Baton Rouge or Lafayette. The interior of this home is sure to impress with its open floor plan that brings together the living, dining, and kitchen areas and its quality craftsmanship throughout. The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a pantry closet and an island with seating. The master suite is complete with a walk-in closet and a spacious bathroom with a soaker tub, shower, and double vanities. Other great features of this home include custom pop-up and trayed ceilings throughout, wainscoting, crown molding, stained concrete, and oversized closets. The large yard surrounding this home is perfect for those who appreciate the outdoors. Whether you're looking to create your own garden oasis or provide a spacious play area for children and pets, this property offers the canvas for your outdoor dreams. This space, complete with a covered, open patio and fireplace, provides the ideal backdrop for gatherings, barbecues, and outdoor fun with friends and loved ones. Home is eligible for 100% financing. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this home your own!
